# Copy to `.env.local` for local overrides (Vite).
#
# PawBot does **not** use a browser API key. The SPA calls `POST /api/chat/stream`
# on the PawHub API; configure Gemini on the server:
#   `pawhub.gemini.api-key` and `pawhub.gemini.whisker-model` in backend `application.yml`
#   (or env vars `PAWHUB_GEMINI_API_KEY`, etc. if you map them).
#
# Optional — only if you later add a client-side Gemini route (not used by default):
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=
